similar_used.approach_summary:
The solution uses the property that $$
\sum_{k=0}^n {^{m-k}C_r} = {^{m+1}C_{r+1}} - {^{m-n}C_{r+1}}
$$ to arrive at the final answer. It rewrites the summation by reversing the order of terms. Then it uses the identity ${ }^{n} C_{r}+{ }^{n} C_{r-1}={ }^{n+1} C_{r}$ to simplify the sum, which leads to the final answer.
